パッケージ com.shimizukenta.secs.local.property

インタフェース StringProperty

すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
java.lang.CharSequence, java.lang.Comparable<StringGettable>, Gettable<java.lang.String>, Observable<java.lang.String>, Property<java.lang.String>, java.io.Serializable, Settable<java.lang.String>, StringGettable, StringObservable, StringSettable
public interface StringProperty
extends Property<java.lang.String>, StringGettable, StringSettable, StringObservable
String value Property, includes Getter, Setter, Observer.

This interface deny null inputs. If input null, replace to empty string.

  • To build instance, newInstance()
  • To set value, StringSettable.set(CharSequence)
  • To toString(), CharSequence.toString()
  • To detect value changed, Observable.addChangeListener(ChangeListener)
  • To compute,
    • StringObservable.computeIsEmpty().
    • StringObservable.computeIsNotEmpty()
    • StringObservable.computeContains(CharSequence)
    • StringObservable.computeTrim()
    • StringObservable.computeToUpperCase()
    • StringObservable.computeToLowerCase()
    • StringObservable.computeMatches(String)
    • StringObservable.computeLength()
  • To wait until condition is true,
    • StringObservable.waitUntilIsEmpty()
    • StringObservable.waitUntilIsNotEmptyAndGet()
    • StringObservable.waitUntilEqualTo(StringObservable)
    • StringObservable.waitUntilEqualToIgnoreCase(StringObservable)
関連項目:
StringGettable, StringSettable, StringObservable, Property
